Title: An Act Changing the Name of Southern District Hospital in the Municipality of Kiblawan, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Gregorio Matas District Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 757
An Act Changing the Name of Southern District Hospital in the Municipality of Kiblawan, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Gregorio Matas District Hospital
Section 1. The name of Southern District Hospital in the Municipality of Kiblawan, Province of Davao del Sur, is hereby changed to Gregorio Matas District Hospital.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
